videos.headline: Alabama shuts the door on Ole Miss onside kick
videos.description: Ole Miss fails on its onside kick attempt with under two minutes in the fourth quarter vs. Alabama.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Alabama shuts the door on Ole Miss onside kick) 2020/10/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ole Miss kicker can't hang on to onside kick recovery
videos.description: Ole Miss place kicker Luke Logan lets the football fall through is arms on a failed onside kick attempt vs. Alabama.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ole Miss kicker can't hang on to onside kick recovery) 2020/10/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harris goes off for 5 TDs as Bama puts away Ole Miss
videos.description: Najee Harris runs all over Ole Miss' defense, scoring five touchdowns on 206 rushing yards in Alabama's 63-48 win.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Harris goes off for 5 TDs as Bama puts away Ole Miss) 2020/10/10 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Saban and Alabama outlast Kiffin and Ole Miss in thriller
videos.description: It's offense galore as Alabama outlasts Ole Miss 63-48 and Nick Saban improves to 21-0 against his former assistants, including Lane Kiffin.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Saban and Alabama outlast Kiffin and Ole Miss in thriller) 2020/10/10 ESHEET SOTFULL
